cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.MA 

The paper proposes a novel reinforcement learning-based framework for online advertising in recommendation systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which is the primary focus of the paper. The paper also deals with information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it involves optimizing the recommendation list and determining the optimal ad and location to interpolate. The paper also involves data structures (cs.DS) as it deals with designing a Deep Q-network architecture. Finally, the paper involves multi-agent systems (cs.MA) as it deals with optimizing the rec/ads trade-off.
